{"tid":562361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【伊斯蘭文化】馬來西亞慶新年裝飾，唔畀有「狗」。","createTime":"2018-02-15T23:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T16:16:31.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed70db951d38cb02ff18f1d7a1cd3f9aae56f7e","tid":562361,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T23:21:50.000Z","msg":"狗年來臨，馬來西亞不少商場近日換上農曆新年裝飾，&hellip;&hellip;唯獨未見任何狗的圖案。以香港為基地的牛奶國際（Dairy Farm International Holdings）旗下的連鎖超市Giant亦推出一款賀年T恤，衣上印有十二生肖圖案，但狗和豬均只是以「亥」和「戌」的字眼代替。<br />\n<br />\n根據伊斯蘭教傳統，狗和豬均是「不潔的動物」，而大馬人口當中穆斯林民眾為數不少，因此當地華裔商人預備狗年裝飾時選擇避之則吉，放棄以狗的圖案作為裝飾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180215/large/1518664283_e723.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180215%2Flarge%2F1518664283_e723.jpg&d=XOKAt4ezNOtiMvOg3FSiiL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=0d697175\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180215/large/1518664283_e723.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"aeb45f53888beba354c6f31f563253cd7f874005","tid":562361,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T23:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfde22dbf468bee3b366aa3646a4cd8a10874acd","tid":562361,"uid":52605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T00:00:44.000Z","msg":"穆斯林養工作犬可以 、養寵物狗禁止<br />\n更加禁止食狗肉<br />\n有D教派比狗惦到要洗七次 有D教派甚至話狗有損功德"},{"pid":"aebffbb9223ce96c14781afe7ee1878fa4da54d8","tid":562361,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T00:18:39.000Z","msg":"無聽過"},{"pid":"0e31f9be8512650ad9deaf44cd4f7e335e8df59f","tid":562361,"uid":29804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:21:31.000Z","msg":"事實係嗰間鋪頭自我閹割<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞郵局有出狗年郵票"},{"pid":"72948d8fdead2734e7edabc7f4952ef9ec0fb70c","tid":562361,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi