Cy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=349b248a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2018/01/17/new-stamp-series-pays-tribute-to-working-dogs/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thestar.com.my/~/media/online/2018/01/16/19/13/main_ha_1701_p8_hazlin_2.ashx/?w=620&amp;h=413&amp;crop=1&amp;hash=45D9AD080159DE65AD101E131649CF8896AD53F8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestar.com.my%2F~%2Fmedia%2Fonline%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F19%2F13%2Fmain_ha_1701_p8_hazlin_2.ashx%2F%3Fw%3D620%26h%3D413%26crop%3D1%26hash%3D45D9AD080159DE65AD101E131649CF8896AD53F8&h=844bb441&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n班伊斯蘭人無嘈咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又話不潔？<br />\n<br />\n係咪無伊斯蘭人會買呢款郵票？"},{"pid":"2d5ae7cbb0386bcc66ba878bfa19e8e2d121be81","tid":562361,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:39:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://johor.chinapress.com.my/20180118/友族也愛不釋手-服務犬郵票一早賣完/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjohor.chinapress.com.my%2F20180118%2F%E5%8F%8B%E6%97%8F%E4%B9%9F%E6%84%9B%E4%B8%8D%E9%87%8B%E6%89%8B-%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E7%8A%AC%E9%83%B5%E7%A5%A8%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A9%E8%B3%A3%E5%AE%8C%2F&d=XOKAt4ezNOtiMvOg3FSiiL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=c8836932\" target=\"_blank\">http://johor.chinapress.com.my/20180118/友族也愛不釋手-服務犬郵票一早賣完/</a><br />\n<br />\n友族也愛不釋手 &ldquo;服務犬&rdquo;郵票一早賣完<br />\n<br />\n（新山18日訊）狗年到，代表&ldquo;旺旺&rdquo;，馬來西亞郵政局配合狗年在全國郵政局限量發售&ldquo;服務犬&rdquo;系列郵票，除了吸引華裔集郵發燒友購買，<span style=\"color: red;\">一些友族也不避忌</span>，愛不釋手。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞郵政局共推出5款設計郵票，每款郵票面值60仙，各款限量發售20萬張，小全張郵票設計為警察與德國牧羊犬和進行搜毒工作的拉布拉多犬，各限量發售2萬5000張。<br />\n<br />\n3款一套郵票售價1令吉90仙，包含首日封售價2令吉45仙，小全張每張售價5令吉30仙、包含首日封售價5令吉85仙。<br />\n<br />\n《中國報》今日走訪位于新山郵政總局了解，有人大清早6時就開始陸陸續續前來排隊，郵政局于上午8時30分開門正式發售&ldquo;服務犬&rdquo;系列郵票，上午10時左右全部售完。<br />\n<br />\n現場發現，華裔購買者有老中青外，<span style=\"color: red;\">至少有6名巫裔也沒避忌前來購買這系列郵票</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16490ca457c6894aa4c58168579850e6d2e11db","tid":562361,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:42:07.000Z","msg":"唔知有幾多友族食過肉骨茶呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7669e8b77d3f35fc43ad63353b170eec225a0d77","tid":562361,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知有幾多友族食過肉骨茶呢&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/cny/dog2.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote>其實班伊斯蘭人係咪會靜靜雞食豬？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我見果d印印去酒樓都照食有豬既點心"},{"pid":"5b2719c853c0f66b8739871121e935c9cf6ecbd9","tid":562361,"uid":56701,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:51:20.000Z","msg":"呢個世界最不潔嘅，係成日以為自己好神聖，但就話人地不潔嘅死賤種垃圾教派"},{"pid":"2f40b85c0faa66f7f11c67935ebc50256a351675","tid":562361,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7669e8b77d3f35fc43ad63353b170eec225a0d77","tid":562361,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知有幾多友族食過肉骨茶呢&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/cny/dog2.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote>其實班伊斯蘭人係咪會靜靜雞食豬？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我見果d印印去酒樓都照食有豬既點心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"No<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIt's 珍珠雞<br />\nChicken only<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1947084879863adeb66427c4285e33f06e9a0c","tid":562361,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔知有幾多友族食過肉骨茶呢&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/cny/dog2.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote>其實班伊斯蘭人係咪會靜靜雞食豬？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我見果d印印去酒樓都照食有豬既點心</blockquote>No&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/cny/no.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; <br